    <p>Help us build a foundation for the platform cooperative movement.</p> 

		<p>The mission of the project is to help birth a new generation of cooperatives using crowdfunding technology that enables supporters to seed cooperatives with new members and fresh capital.</p>

		<p>Our plan is to help usher in a new era of social venture funding where investments are people-powered and our economic systems are cooperatively owned.</p>

